  <sections xmi:id="_sIfvkEmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw" name="Define the education deliverables" guid="_sIfvkEmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw">
    <sectionName>Define the education deliverables</sectionName>
    <sectionDescription>Obtain agreement on education work products, and set client expectations regarding the work products that should be&#xD;
produced to support education and training. Show samples of education work products to the client to get an understanding&#xD;
of the client's needs and expectations. Provide a definition of the electronic and hardcopy information that will be&#xD;
produced to support the education tasks.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_xNf6gEmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw" name="Define the education and training responsibilities" guid="_xNf6gEmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw">
    <sectionName>Define the education and training responsibilities</sectionName>
    <sectionDescription>Establish who will have the responsibility for providing the trainers and facilities, and for producing the education&#xD;
materials.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_3IRP0EmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw" name="Develop end-user documentation plan" guid="_3IRP0EmxEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw">
    <sectionName>Develop end-user documentation plan</sectionName>
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    End-user documentation is developed primarily from the detailed scripting documents produced in the analysis and design&#xD;
    phases of the project. Establish an early understanding as to what is to be generated and by whom. Also determine what&#xD;
    end-user documentation is to be produced.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Specify the following:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        End-user documentation scope to get an early understanding of end-user documentation needs.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        End-user documentation approach.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        End-user documentation work products.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;div style=&quot;LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none&quot;>&#xD;
            End-user documentation responsibilities.&#xD;
        &lt;/div>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_cQ5vUEmyEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw" name="Compile the training and end-user procedure strategy document" guid="_cQ5vUEmyEdy1dqDW7Ktmiw">
    <sectionName>Compile the training and end-user procedure strategy document</sectionName>
    <sectionDescription xsi:nil="true"/>
  </sections>
  <purpose>Develop (at a high level) the education deliverables and responsibilities of the client, so that effective education&#xD;
planning and preparation can proceed. &lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;br />&#xD;
Obtain the client's concurrence.</purpose>
  <alternatives xsi:nil="true"/>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
